OL,6,FAlex Probyn, president of property tax
OL,7,Fat Altus Group, warned of a "double
OL,8,Fwhammy" of property tax rises for pubs
OL,9,Fnext April, calling on Chancellor
OL,10,FRachel Reeves to use her autumn Budget
OL,11,Fon October 30 to extend the business
OL,12,Frates relief.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the British Beer
OL,15,Fand Pub Association said: "While we
OL,16,Fknow that brewers and pubs pour
OL,17,Fbillions into the economy, their
OL,18,Fmassive contribution to society is
OL,19,Fpriceless which is why any closure is
OL,20,Fdevastating.
